@startuml seq-add-internal-contact
' Context: contacts
' SDD: PROM-PERSONAL-CONTACTS-011
' Revision: 2026-07-19

title Contacts — aggiunta contatto internal (Alfred)

actor Utente
participant "UI" as UI
participant "ContactsMachine" as CM
participant "ContactService" as Svc
participant "Supabase" as DB

Utente -> UI : cerca utente
UI -> CM : SearchProfiles(query)
CM -> Svc : searchProfiles(query)
Svc -> DB : search_profiles
DB --> Svc : profile summaries
Svc --> CM : results
CM --> UI : ProfileSearchResults

Utente -> UI : seleziona profilo
UI -> CM : AddInternalContact(profile)
CM -> Svc : addInternalContact(owner, profile)
Svc -> DB : INSERT contact (internal)
DB --> Svc : row
Svc --> CM : ContactAdded

CM -> CM : LoadContacts
CM -> Svc : fetchContacts(owner)
Svc -> DB : SELECT contacts
DB --> Svc : rows
Svc --> CM : ContactsLoaded
CM --> UI : rubrica aggiornata

@enduml
